data.description: Amazing 3/2 home in Jupiter Farms with 2 car attached garage and also 2 stall barn in the back yard sitting on 1.13 acres. House has an open floor plan with enormous kitchen and island. The kitchen has new s/s appliances, brand new hood over the stove. The entire home has new waterproof vinyl flooring throughout, newer baseboards and the entire inside and outside of the home has been recently  painted.The yard is fully fenced and has gate. TheBack Patio is completely screened in and is great for entertaining. This wonderful home is ready for new owners and will not last!. This home also is on a paved road and the only roads to this home are all paved.
